body:
We started running into this issue when doing a `go mod tidy` 

```
❯ go build
# go.temporal.io/sdk/client
/Users/camiloaguilar/go/pkg/mod/go.temporal.io/sdk@v1.15.0/client/service_proxy.go:50:9: cannot use &workflowServiceProxyServer{…} (value of type *workflowServiceProxyServer) as type workflowservice.WorkflowServiceServer in return statement:
	*workflowServiceProxyServer does not implement workflowservice.WorkflowServiceServer (missing GetWorkerBuildIdOrdering method)
```
title: sdk 1.15.0 seems to be incompatible with go.temporal.io/api v1.9.0
